      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来构建这个结构。起点是HealthTech_PatientRecords，然后Idle→Loading由Start Request触发，Loading→Success是Data Received，Loading→Error是Request Failed。",
      "elements_involved": [
